text: Henri Edward Jeanneret (1 January 1878 – 1 June 1935) was a Swiss-born Australian rules footballer who played in the Victorian Football League (VFL). ==Playing career== A wingman, Jeanneret made his debut for South Melbourne in Round 1 of the 1898 VFL season. After 75 matches for South Melbourne over six seasons, he moved to Melbourne for the 1904 VFL season.
